FBIS3-34843 "drnes032dd_94002" FBIS-NES-94-032 Document Type:Daily Report 16 Feb 1994 Palestinian Affairs 'Arafat Reportedly Deposits Funds in Wife's Name NC1502190294 Beirut AL-'AHD in Arabic 4 Feb 94 p 17 NC1502190294 Beirut AL-'AHD Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] Palestinian sources have stated that Yasir 'Arafat has registered large amounts of PLO funds in the name of his wife, Suha Tawil. These funds were originally in 'Arafat's name. The sources said large amounts, estimated at millions of dollars, have been placed in Suha Tawil's name in Asian banks and investment companies, including ones in Singapore and Indonesia.
